race.comment: KEEP ON RUNNING (3) came home strongly last start beaten 0.6 lengths over 1609m at this track. Improved off the win prior here over a sprint and is a decent chance to bounce. WHIRLWIND (6) returned from a break with a solid 2.6L defeat last start at Mackay over 1200m after she gave away a big start. Has switched from a Victorian stable and won't be bothered by this longer journey. Fitter and expected to run well back in grade. KOBAYASTAR (13) hasn't been beaten far since resuming with market confidence. Has placed 3/3 third-up and tumbles in weight this grade. That brings her into it. IMPRESSIONISM (2) resumes and won a 58 here when last seen. He will use the inside gate and will be every chance to run out 1400m.
